11#include "modules/audio_processing/high_pass_filter.h"

13#include "api/array_view.h"
14#include "modules/audio_processing/audio_buffer.h"
15#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19namespace {
20// [B,A] = butter(2,100/8000,'high')
21constexpr CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadCoefficients
22 kHighPassFilterCoefficients16kHz = {{0.97261f, -1.94523f, 0.97261f},
23 {-1.94448f, 0.94598f}};
24
25// [B,A] = butter(2,100/16000,'high')
26constexpr CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadCoefficients
27 kHighPassFilterCoefficients32kHz = {{0.98621f, -1.97242f, 0.98621f},
28 {-1.97223f, 0.97261f}};
29
30// [B,A] = butter(2,100/24000,'high')
31constexpr CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadCoefficients
32 kHighPassFilterCoefficients48kHz = {{0.99079f, -1.98157f, 0.99079f},
33 {-1.98149f, 0.98166f}};
34
35constexpr size_t kNumberOfHighPassBiQuads = 1;
36
37const CascadedBiQuadFilter::BiQuadCoefficients& ChooseCoefficients(
38 int sample_rate_hz) {
39 switch (sample_rate_hz) {
40 case 16000:
41 return kHighPassFilterCoefficients16kHz;
42 case 32000:
43 return kHighPassFilterCoefficients32kHz;
44 case 48000:
45 return kHighPassFilterCoefficients48kHz;
46 default:
47 RTC_NOTREACHED();
48 }
49 RTC_NOTREACHED();
50 return kHighPassFilterCoefficients16kHz;
51}
52
53} // namespace
54
55HighPassFilter::HighPassFilter(int sample_rate_hz, size_t num_channels)
56 : sample_rate_hz_(sample_rate_hz) {
57 filters_.resize(num_channels);
58 const auto& coefficients = ChooseCoefficients(sample_rate_hz_);
59 for (size_t k = 0; k < filters_.size(); ++k) {
60 filters_[k].reset(
61 new CascadedBiQuadFilter(coefficients, kNumberOfHighPassBiQuads));
62 }
63}
64
65HighPassFilter::~HighPassFilter() = default;
66
67void HighPassFilter::Process(AudioBuffer* audio, bool use_split_band_data) {
68 RTC_DCHECK(audio);
69 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(filters_.size(), audio->num_channels());
70 if (use_split_band_data) {
71 for (size_t k = 0; k < audio->num_channels(); ++k) {
72 rtc::ArrayView<float> channel_data = rtc::ArrayView<float>(
73 audio->split_bands(k)[0], audio->num_frames_per_band());
74 filters_[k]->Process(channel_data);
75 }
76 } else {
77 for (size_t k = 0; k < audio->num_channels(); ++k) {
78 rtc::ArrayView<float> channel_data =
79 rtc::ArrayView<float>(&audio->channels()[k][0], audio->num_frames());
80 filters_[k]->Process(channel_data);
81 }
82 }
83}
84
85void HighPassFilter::Process(std::vector<std::vector<float>>* audio) {
86 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(filters_.size(), audio->size());
87 for (size_t k = 0; k < audio->size(); ++k) {
88 filters_[k]->Process((*audio)[k]);
89 }
90}
91
92void HighPassFilter::Reset() {
93 for (size_t k = 0; k < filters_.size(); ++k) {
94 filters_[k]->Reset();
95 }
96}
97
98void HighPassFilter::Reset(size_t num_channels) {
99 const size_t old_num_channels = filters_.size();
100 filters_.resize(num_channels);
101 if (filters_.size() < old_num_channels) {
102 Reset();
103 } else {
104 for (size_t k = 0; k < old_num_channels; ++k) {
105 filters_[k]->Reset();
106 }
107 const auto& coefficients = ChooseCoefficients(sample_rate_hz_);
108 for (size_t k = old_num_channels; k < filters_.size(); ++k) {
109 filters_[k].reset(
110 new CascadedBiQuadFilter(coefficients, kNumberOfHighPassBiQuads));
111 }
112 }
113}
